        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 13
      },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Runtime Notes\nThis dashboard focuses on the edge cases we care about in a pause/resume chat runtime:\n- provider header latency\n- pause effective latency\n- SSE disconnects\n- Langfuse score delivery health\n\nPromQL uses `__name__` regexes on purpose so the templates remain usable whether your backend exposes OTel counters with or without `_total` / `_milliseconds` suffix translation.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Template Notes",
      "type": "text"
    }
